# Podman + GPU Acceleration One-Click Setup
Automated setup for rootless Podman with GPU acceleration on **Arch Linux / CachyOS**  
Supports NVIDIA, AMD, and Intel GPUs.

## Features
- Installs and configures rootless Podman
- Automatic GPU detection (NVIDIA / AMD / Intel)
- Persistent udev rules for GPU permissions
- Proper subuid / subgid mapping
- NVIDIA Container Toolkit integration
- Enables linger for user-level systemd services

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/TheChronoClaw/CachyOS-OpenClaw-Podman-one-click-hardening-script.git
cd CachyOS-OpenClaw-Podman-one-click-hardening-script
chmod +x setup-podman-gpu.sh
sudo ./setup-podman-gpu.sh
